        "keywords": "Astronomical data,Clustering high-dimensional data,Connected morphological operators,H.3.3 [information search and retrieval]: clusteri,I.3.6 [computer graphics]: methodology and techniq,J.2 [computer applications]: physical sciences and,Subspace finding,Visual exploration,:Used in Analysis,Has VS:Summary Design,Data Abstraction:Aggregation,Data Abstraction:Filtering",
        "link": "http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/lpdocs/epic03/wrapper.htm?arnumber",
        "month": "oct",
        "pages": "35--42",
