        "keywords": "Boxplots,Uncertainty visualization,band depth,ensemble visualization,order statistics,:Used in Analysis,Has VS:Summary Design,Purpose:Exploration,Purpose:Confirmation,Purpose:Presentation,Data Abstraction:Aggregation,Data Abstraction:Filtering,Task Means - Relation:Comparison,Task Means - Relation:Variations,Task Characteristics - High-Level:Trends,Task Characteristics - High-Level:Distribution",
